  characterName: Llora
  portrait: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueLines:
  - Have you met my father Taul yet?
  - He's this town's butcher!
  - I'm so proud of father!
  - He honestly works so hard on his meat.
  - Maybe one day I can be like him.
  - Do you think I'd be able to take over this shop one day?
  - Don't answer that, I don't want my future to be spoiled just yet.
  - You should really go and meet father.
  - He really is just THE best.
